caption:
Did you know that plums are part of the rose family? It’s like each nutrient-rich bite is a gesture of self-love 🌹 

When you snack on plums, here’s how you’re caring for your body:

🤍 Vitamin C helps the body produce essential collagen and strengthens your immune system
🤍 Fiber supports healthy digestion and gut wellness
🤍 Potassium helps maintain heart health and balanced blood pressure
🤍 Antioxidants protect your cells from harmful free radicals
🤍 Vitamin K and polyphenols reduce bone loss and support bone formation
